  "texts": [
    "All tasks for the model and all answers are shown in Supplementary Note 1.",
    "First, we evaluated the agent's ability to recognize and successfully use tools (Fig. 4).",
    "Of 64 required tool invocations to fully solve all given patient cases, the agent correctly used 56, achieving an overall success rate of 87.5%, with no failures among the required tools.",
    "The remaining 12.5% of tools were required but missed by the model.",
    "There were two instances where the model tried to call superfluous tools without the necessary data available, which resulted in failures (Fig. 4, 'tool use')."
  ],
